: [121.9, 786.2, 1158.3, 807.0]}, {"text": "of $36.2 million.", "bbox": [121.9, 805.0, 248.0, 825.8]}, {"text": "(2)", "bbox": [84.4, 829.4, 103.3, 852.9]}, {"text": "Net income (loss) per share is computed independently. Therefore, the sum of the quarterly net income per share may not equal the total", "bbox": [121.9, 832.1, 1158.3, 852.9]}, {"text": "computed for the year or any cumulative interim period.", "bbox": [121.9, 850.8, 543.3, 871.6]}, {"text": "(3)", "bbox": [84.4, 875.3, 103.3, 898.7]}, {"text": "Potentially dilutive common shares for the fourth quarter of 2017 were excluded from the computation of diluted net loss per share because", "bbox": [121.9, 877.9, 1158.3, 898.7]}, {"text": "their effect would be anti-dilutive.", "bbox": [121.9, 896.7, 378.4, 917.5]}, {"text": "Note 18. Subsequent Events", "bbox": [84.4, 942.4, 331.1, 965.4]}, {"text": "Dividend Declaration", "bbox": [84.4, 992.4, 269.1, 1015.4]}, {"text": "On January 30, 2018, the Company announced that the Board declared a quarterly cash dividend of $0.18 per share of common", "bbox": [84.4, 1042.4, 1158.8, 1065.5]}, {"text": "stock to be paid on March 22, 2018 to stockholders of record as of the close of business on March 1, 2018. This reflects an increase", "bbox": [84.4, 1067.4, 1158.8, 1090.5]}, {"text": "of 80% compared to previous quarterly dividends.", "bbox": [84.4, 1092.4, 508.1, 1115.5]}, {"text": "Stock Repurchase Activities", "bbox": [84.4, 1142.4, 322.2, 1165.5]}, {"text": "In January 2018, the Board approved a new $2.0 billion share repurchase authorization (\"2018 Stock Repurchase Program\"), which", "bbox": [84.4, 1192.4, 1158.8, 1215.5]}, {"text": "replaces the previous authorization. The Board also authorized the Company to enter into an accelerated share repurchase program", "bbox": [84.4, 1217.4, 1158.8, 1240.5]}, {"text": "(\"ASR\") for an amount up to $750.0 million under the 2018 Stock Repurchase Program.", "bbox": [84.4, 1242.4, 820.9, 1265.5]}, {"text": "In February 2018, the Company entered into ASR agreements with two financial institutions to repurchase an aggregate of $750.0", "bbox": [84.4, 1292.5, 1158.8, 1315.5]}, {"text": "million of the Company's common stock. The Company made an up-front payment of $750.0 million pursuant to the ASR and", "bbox": [84.4, 1317.5, 1158.8, 1340.5]}, {"text": "received and retired an initial 23.3 million shares of the Company's common stock for an aggregate price of $600.0 million based", "bbox": [84.4, 1342.5, 1158.8, 1365.5]}, {"text": "on the market value of the Company's common stock on the date of the transaction. The Company has an aggregate of $1.3 billion", "bbox": [84.4, 1367.5, 1153.6, 1390.6]}, {"text": "of authorized funds remaining under the 2018 Stock Repurchase Program, as of the filing date of this Annual Report on Form 10-", "bbox": [84.4, 1392.5, 1153.6, 1415.6]}, {"text": "K.", "bbox": [84.4, 1417.5, 109.9, 1440.6]}, {"text": "Future share repurchases under the 2018 Stock Repurchase Program will be subject to a review of the circumstances at that time", "bbox": [84.4, 1467.5, 1158.8, 1490.6]}, {"text": "and will be made from time to time in private transactions or open market purchases as permitted by securities laws and other", "bbox": [84.4, 1492.5, 1158.8, 1515.6]}, {"text": "legal requirements. The Company's 2018 Stock Repurchase Program may be discontinued at any time.", "bbox": [84.4, 1517.5, 944.4, 1540.6]}]}